text: Mary Milne (1914-2014) married name Dumbrill, was a female athlete who competed for England. ==Athletics career== She competed for England in the high jump at the 1934 British Empire Games in London. Milne was a three times AAA outdoor champion. ==Personal life== Mary Milne married Leonard Dumbrill in 1935. ==References== Category:1914 births Category:2014 deaths Category:English female high jumpers Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1934 British Empire Games
